  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200&deg;C/ 180&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 6</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>sweet potatoes</strong>&nbsp;(skins on) into&nbsp;wedges</p>\r\n<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>wedges</strong>&nbsp;to a baking tray with a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>vegetable oil&nbsp;</strong>and a generous pinch of&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;and give everything a good old mix up</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until the&nbsp;wedges&nbsp;are golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Drain and rinse the<strong> kidney beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong>&nbsp;<strong>kidney&nbsp;beans, chipotle paste,</strong>&nbsp;<strong>smoked paprika</strong>, a very generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>to a pot&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Mash until smooth</p>\r\n<p>Tip: <span class=\"text-highlight\">you</span> can use a bowl with a flat bottom instead</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>grated cheese</strong> to the pot and give everything a good old mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>bean mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>bean mix</strong>&nbsp;between the <strong>tortilla wraps </strong>and spread it out&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Fold each&nbsp;<strong>tortilla</strong>&nbsp;<strong>wrap</strong>&nbsp;over so you're left with 6 crescent-shaped sandwiches&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong>&nbsp;folded tortilla wraps</strong>&nbsp;to a second baking tray</p>\r\n<p>Place the <strong>sweet potato baking tray</strong> on top of the&nbsp;<strong>tortilla baking tray</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the stacked baking trays in the oven and cook for 15-20 min further or until the&nbsp;tortillas&nbsp;are slightly browned and the cheese is melted</p>\r\n<p>Tip: <span class=\"text-highlight\">once</span> the tortillas have 5 min left, remove the sweet potato tray from the tortilla tray and return both trays to the oven separately, allowing the tortillas to crisp slightly&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim and slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> finely, keeping the white and green&nbsp;ends separate&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>mayonnaise</strong>, <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and&nbsp;the white&nbsp;ends of the <strong>spring onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; this is your <strong>spring onion dip</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1667.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tortilla</strong>&nbsp;<strong>bean melts</strong> with the<strong> sweet potato wedges</strong> and <strong>spring onion</strong> <strong>dip</strong> to the side&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved&nbsp;green spring onion</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
  ],
